1. *Nigdje* ne mogu da nađem svoje ključeve. (Nowhere can I find my keys.)
2. Ne želim da idem *nigdje*. (I don't want to go anywhere.)
3. Ona je *nigdje* iznenada se pojavila. (She suddenly appeared out of nowhere.)
4. Da li si video moju torbu? Ne mogu da je nađem *nigdje*. (Have you seen my bag? I can't find it anywhere.)
5. Sve vreme sam se vozio gradom i *nigdje* nisam mogao da nađem parkirno mesto. (I drove around the city the whole time and couldn't find a parking spot anywhere.)
6. *Nigdje* nisam čuo takvu priču. (Nowhere have I heard such a story.)
7. U ovoj knjizi *nigdje* ne piše o tome. (In this book, there's nowhere written about it.)
8. *Nigdje* drugde nećete naći ovakvu hranu. (You won't find this kind of food anywhere else.)

Note: The word "nigdje" in Serbian is equivalent to "nowhere" or "anywhere" in English. It can be used as an adverb, a pronoun or as a part of a prepositional phrase.